{
  "texts": [
    "These analyses can be made more efficient by strengthening the CNN architecture and increasing the magnitude of the dataset.",
    "Marzban et al. (2020) developed a robust method for classifying MCI and AD against HC.",
    "This system is designed to operate on a low-cost network, characterized by a shallow architecture and efficient processing.",
    "CNN is used as the classification algorithm, with grey matter volumes and diffusion maps as input images.",
    "It demonstrates the significance of integrating data from diverse imaging modalities such as sMRI, diffusion tensor imaging (DTI) and elucidates its impact on the overall results."
  ]
}